newsitem.title: AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Bank Melbourne sees satisfactory results.
newsitem.headline: RTRS-Bank Melbourne sees satisfactory results.

text.p: Bank of Melbourne Ltd chairman Christopher Stewart said on Monday that tighter interest margins would impact on the bank's profitability growth.
However, Stewart told the annual meeting that high efficiency and low costs would help deliver a satisfactory result in 1996/97 (July-June).
